---
// Training journey section
---

<section id="training" class="s-training" data-intersect>
  <div class="s__inner">
    <h2 class="s__title">Training Journey</h2>
    <p class="s__subtitle">Strengthening problem-solving skills through intensive specialized training.</p>

    <div class="s-training__card js-card">
      <div class="s-training__content">
        <div class="s-training__header">
          <div class="s-training__icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"></path>
              <path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="s-training__info">
            <h3>Data Structures & Algorithms Training</h3>
            <div class="s-training__meta">
              <span class="s-training__org">Skillstone</span>
              <span class="s-training__date">June 2025 – July 2025</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="s-training__body">
          <p>
            Completed an intensive <strong>Data Structures & Algorithms</strong> training program designed to strengthen algorithmic thinking and advanced problem-solving skills required for software engineering roles.
          </p>
          
          <div class="s-training__highlights">
            <h4><span class="icon">🏆</span> Key Highlights</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Solved <strong>500+ coding problems</strong> on platforms like LeetCode and GeeksforGeeks.</li>
              <li>Mastered advanced concepts including <strong>Trees, Graphs, Dynamic Programming, and Recursion</strong>.</li>
              <li>Focused on designing optimized algorithms and solving real-world complex problems.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="s-training__media">
        <div class="media-container">
          <img src="/images/Screenshot 2025-12-19 at 15.39.19.pdf" alt="Training Certificate Preview" />
          <span class="media-label">Certificate</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  .s-training {
    padding: 10rem 0;
    background: color(primary);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;

    @include mq(phone) {
      padding: 5rem 1rem;
    }

    .s__inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .s__title {
      font: 700 4rem / 1 font-family(bigger);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: color(secondary);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      
      @include mq(phone) {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
    }

    .s__subtitle {
      font: 400 1.2rem / 1.4 font-family(fraktion);
      color: color(secondary);
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 5rem;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .s-training__card {
      display: flex;
      background: rgba(color(secondary), 0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(color(secondary), 0.2);
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      
      @include mq(tablet) {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
    }

    .s-training__content {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 3rem;
      
      @include mq(phone) {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }
    }

    .s-training__header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;

      .s-training__icon {
        background: color(secondary);
        color: color(primary);
        padding: 0.75rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
      }

      h3 {
        font: 700 1.8rem / 1 font-family(fraktion);
        color: color(secondary);
        margin: 0;
        
        @include mq(phone) {
          font-size: 1.4rem;
        }
      }

      .s-training__meta {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-family: font-family(fraktion);
        
        .s-training__org {
          background: rgba(color(secondary), 0.1);
          padding: 2px 8px;
          border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .s-training__date {
          opacity: 0.6;
        }
      }
    }

    .s-training__body {
      color: color(secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 1.1rem;

      p { margin-bottom: 2rem; }

      .s-training__highlights {
        h4 {
          text-transform: uppercase;
          font-size: 0.9rem;
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        ul {
          list-style: none;
          padding: 0;
          
          li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            font-size: 1rem;

            &:before {
              content: '→';
              position: absolute;
              left: 0;
              color: color(secondary);
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }

    .s-training__media {
      flex: 0 0 40%;
      background: rgba(color(secondary), 0.05);
      padding: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      
      @include mq(tablet) {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      .media-container {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        min-height: 250px;
        
        img {
          width: 100%;
          height: 100%;
          object-fit: contain;
          border-radius: 12px;
          border: 1px solid rgba(color(secondary), 0.1);
        }

        .media-label {
          position: absolute;
          top: 10px;
          right: 10px;
          background: color(secondary);
          color: color(primary);
          padding: 2px 8px;
          font-size: 0.7rem;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          border-radius: 4px;
        }
      }
    }
  }
</style>
